WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:01:00.000

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.980
Episode 06

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.510
My mom is from Sichuan,

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:37.000
and my dad is from Zhejiang.

00:01:37.430 --> 00:01:38.870
That's why sometimes

00:01:38.870 --> 00:01:40.510
I say I'm from Sichuan,

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:41.430
and sometimes I say

00:01:41.430 --> 00:01:42.710
I'm from Zhejiang.

00:01:43.510 --> 00:01:45.230
My dad didn't want a girl.

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:46.040
He divorced

00:01:46.070 --> 00:01:47.350
my mom right after I was born.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:49.480
But the funny thing is,

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:51.510
the court gave me to my dad.

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:53.000
When I was a teenager,

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.230
I ran away.

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:55.040
When I finally

00:01:55.070 --> 00:01:56.480
found my mom,

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:59.040
she led a tough life too.

00:01:59.710 --> 00:02:01.400
So she left me with my grandma.

00:02:02.760 --> 00:02:03.870
My grandpa

00:02:04.430 --> 00:02:06.400
collected garbage in the city,

00:02:06.950 --> 00:02:09.080
and my grandma and I

00:02:10.030 --> 00:02:11.750
helped him with it.

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:13.520
I don't care if you make

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:14.360
fun of me.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:17.150
I never went to school.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.960
Well, I went to junior
high school at least.

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:22.470
You're really...

00:02:25.190 --> 00:02:26.910
Sometimes I just wonder

00:02:29.310 --> 00:02:30.360
if there's anyone

00:02:31.870 --> 00:02:33.030
who has a worse life

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:34.710
than me in this world.

00:02:36.590 --> 00:02:37.750
I also used to wish

00:02:39.430 --> 00:02:41.240
I had been born a boy.

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:49.710
But

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:51.430
now I think

00:02:51.870 --> 00:02:53.120
being a girl is better.

00:02:53.470 --> 00:02:55.000
I could make money
when I was a teenager,

00:02:55.470 --> 00:02:56.430
and once I made money,

00:02:56.590 --> 00:02:57.560
I could buy tons of

00:02:57.630 --> 00:02:58.470
pretty clothes.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:00.150
And with pretty clothes,

00:03:00.150 --> 00:03:01.520
I could make even more money.

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:04.710
Qian, you're not engaged in...

00:03:05.630 --> 00:03:07.080
What are you talking about?

00:03:07.910 --> 00:03:09.710
I made money by singing.

00:03:10.430 --> 00:03:12.520
Sometimes I'd dance a bit

00:03:13.190 --> 00:03:14.030
and flirt.

00:03:14.590 --> 00:03:15.360
Sing?

00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:16.630
You're a singer?

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:18.190
A singer my ass!

00:03:18.310 --> 00:03:18.960
If she could sing,

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:20.000
why would she cook here?

00:03:20.840 --> 00:03:21.430
I really came here

00:03:21.430 --> 00:03:22.960
to become a singer.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:24.120
But

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:25.240
everyone is so professional.

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:26.360
They sing so well...

00:03:26.360 --> 00:03:27.630
So I lost my nerve.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:28.840
Then I found out

00:03:28.910 --> 00:03:30.680
even helping in a kitchen here

00:03:30.750 --> 00:03:32.190
paid 1,000 yuan a month.

00:03:32.590 --> 00:03:33.870
I decided not to leave.

00:03:34.520 --> 00:03:35.360
Otherwise,

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.000
how could the three of us

00:03:37.030 --> 00:03:38.280
have met?

00:03:39.150 --> 00:03:40.750
I actually sing pretty well.

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:49.470
♪Sweet honey♪

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:54.190
♪You smile so sweetly♪

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:59.470
♪Like a flower blooming
in the spring breeze♪

00:04:00.310 --> 00:04:04.840
♪Blooming in the spring breeze♪

00:04:11.080 --> 00:04:11.710
(Wang Jia,)

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:14.310
(I've found a job)

00:04:14.310 --> 00:04:15.430
(in Shenzhen.)

00:04:16.270 --> 00:04:17.270
(Everything is fine.)

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:18.950
(Don't worry.)

00:04:20.870 --> 00:04:22.360
(What I care about most is Li Xingke.)

00:04:24.190 --> 00:04:25.560
(Has the verdict come out?)

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:27.510
(Are there)

00:04:27.750 --> 00:04:29.240
(any updates about him at school?)

00:04:30.430 --> 00:04:32.920
(If yes, write to me right away.)

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:34.800
(If there are important letters,)

00:04:34.920 --> 00:04:36.160
(please forward them to me.)

00:04:37.190 --> 00:04:38.310
(I'll give you my address,)

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:40.750
(but please keep it secret.)

00:04:45.830 --> 00:04:46.830
I oppose!

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.390
I strongly oppose

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:51.310
your decision!

00:04:52.310 --> 00:04:53.000
Education is

00:04:53.040 --> 00:04:54.270
about inspiring people.

00:04:54.830 --> 00:04:56.360
But what have you inspired?

00:04:58.190 --> 00:04:59.360
From the very beginning,

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:00.750
you've tried to wipe Han Bin

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:02.720
clean of this whole thing.

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:04.600
You didn't want to
ruin his bright future.

00:05:04.830 --> 00:05:05.950
You even planned to give him

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:07.190
an award for bravery!

00:05:08.190 --> 00:05:08.870
Why?

00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:11.070
Were you influenced by Director Han?

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.630
So you fawn over the powerful

00:05:12.870 --> 00:05:13.950
and bully the weak?

00:05:14.270 --> 00:05:15.830
You didn't even get

00:05:15.830 --> 00:05:17.390
the basic facts straight!

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:19.270
How could people like you

00:05:19.430 --> 00:05:20.920
have the right to be teachers?

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:24.830
Let me tell you.

00:05:24.830 --> 00:05:25.360
This thing

00:05:25.360 --> 00:05:26.600
isn't over yet.

00:05:27.390 --> 00:05:29.120
I will report this to
higher authorities.

00:05:29.720 --> 00:05:30.480
I'm suing you all!

00:05:31.430 --> 00:05:32.920
Vice Mayor Meng, let me explain!

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:34.240
There is no Vice Mayor Meng here,

00:05:34.950 --> 00:05:37.390
only Fang Wanzhi's father.

00:05:46.950 --> 00:05:47.630
What's going on?

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:49.830
Wanzhi's dad is here!

00:05:50.070 --> 00:05:51.000
As expected of a leader,

00:05:51.070 --> 00:05:52.120
he's so articulate.

00:05:52.310 --> 00:05:53.070
He shut

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:54.360
them all up.

00:05:58.120 --> 00:05:59.750
It should be over now.

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:00.680
Okay.

00:06:02.040 --> 00:06:03.430
Wang Jia, this man's here for you!

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:07.040
Hello, Mr. Meng.

00:06:07.630 --> 00:06:08.560
You know me?

00:06:10.190 --> 00:06:11.800
Wanzhi showed me your photo.

00:06:13.950 --> 00:06:15.360
So I came to the right person.

00:06:49.680 --> 00:06:50.190
Excuse me!

00:06:51.560 --> 00:06:52.040
Hello?

00:06:55.070 --> 00:06:55.870
Sorry I'm late.

00:06:56.190 --> 00:06:57.510
Sorry, I didn't hear you.

00:07:02.360 --> 00:07:02.750
Okay.

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:30.680
Who's that?

00:07:32.310 --> 00:07:33.070
No idea.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:34.870
Why do you look

00:07:34.870 --> 00:07:35.920
so tired?

00:07:36.830 --> 00:07:38.190
Maybe I slept too late.

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:39.950
But I'm getting used to it.

00:07:41.800 --> 00:07:42.800
Your hand...

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:50.390
This...

00:07:51.040 --> 00:07:52.120
It's nothing.

00:07:56.240 --> 00:07:57.270
Let's go home.

00:07:58.630 --> 00:07:59.360
No.

00:07:59.920 --> 00:08:01.120
I signed a labor contract.

00:08:01.310 --> 00:08:02.000
I can't leave.

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:04.430
You're my daughter.

00:08:05.070 --> 00:08:06.270
You didn't even finish college.

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:10.310
Instead, you left home
to be a migrant worker

00:08:11.190 --> 00:08:12.750
and work as a helper
in a construction

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:13.430
site cafeteria.

00:08:14.630 --> 00:08:15.310
I know

00:08:15.390 --> 00:08:16.870
all jobs are equal,

00:08:19.430 --> 00:08:20.310
but I feel

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:21.720
terrible inside.

00:08:23.390 --> 00:08:24.800
I'm such a failure

00:08:25.430 --> 00:08:26.270
as a father.

00:08:27.310 --> 00:08:28.190
I really failed.

00:08:30.920 --> 00:08:31.510
About that matter,

00:08:31.560 --> 00:08:32.550
I was too imprudent.

00:08:35.550 --> 00:08:36.910
I didn't even learn about

00:08:36.910 --> 00:08:38.030
everything that happened

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:41.550
before losing temper with you.

00:08:42.150 --> 00:08:42.870
I'm sorry.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.030
I owe you a proper apology.

00:08:45.870 --> 00:08:46.600
No, no...

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:48.600
I'm the one who should apologize.

00:08:51.870 --> 00:08:53.630
I caused you trouble.

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.080
So how did they

00:08:57.320 --> 00:08:58.000
handle that matter?

00:08:59.390 --> 00:09:00.270
My superiors didn't

00:09:00.390 --> 00:09:01.510
approve my resignation.

00:09:01.960 --> 00:09:03.320
So I'm still in my old position.

00:09:04.960 --> 00:09:05.550
Han Shuang is

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:07.390
under investigation
by an investigation team.

00:09:07.910 --> 00:09:08.630
Your tape

00:09:08.630 --> 00:09:10.240
played a key role.

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:12.440
What about Xingke?

00:09:14.510 --> 00:09:15.030
He'll serve

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:16.550
three years.

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:18.600
Since it's a criminal offense,

00:09:19.150 --> 00:09:20.240
the college can't keep

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:21.000
his student status.

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:25.360
I went to see him once.

00:09:26.910 --> 00:09:28.030
You visited him?

00:09:30.440 --> 00:09:31.510
I tried

00:09:33.510 --> 00:09:35.270
to help you at the school,

00:09:37.910 --> 00:09:39.080
but it didn't go well.

00:09:47.270 --> 00:09:48.080
I understand.

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:51.670
By the school rules,

00:09:52.790 --> 00:09:54.360
I would definitely be expelled.

00:09:55.240 --> 00:09:55.840
It's okay.

00:09:56.870 --> 00:09:58.030
I'll take the exam again later.

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:01.480
Xingke,

00:10:03.390 --> 00:10:05.550
you were always a good student.

00:10:05.910 --> 00:10:07.630
You applied to this college

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:11.480
just to be with Wanzhi, right?

00:10:15.870 --> 00:10:16.600
I didn't do well.

00:10:19.510 --> 00:10:20.480
I even got her into trouble.

00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:31.550
Mr. Meng,

00:10:33.670 --> 00:10:36.600
Wanzhi's best friend is Wang Jia.

00:10:39.030 --> 00:10:39.600
She must know

00:10:39.600 --> 00:10:40.510
where Wanzhi is.

00:10:41.440 --> 00:10:43.080
Please don't blame Wang Jia.

00:10:44.630 --> 00:10:46.360
I found her and begged her

00:10:47.510 --> 00:10:48.550
to give me your address.

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:51.870
Wanzhi,

00:10:52.750 --> 00:10:53.670
tell you what?

00:10:54.870 --> 00:10:56.510
Every day since you left home,

00:10:58.670 --> 00:11:00.550
I've been blaming myself.

00:11:02.480 --> 00:11:03.550
So come home with me.

00:11:04.910 --> 00:11:06.030
I'm doing fine now.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:07.670
Really.

00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:09.150
This is the first time

00:11:09.150 --> 00:11:10.480
I've found a job on my own.

00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:11.870
I can't quit halfway.

00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:13.390
But you have to

00:11:13.390 --> 00:11:14.790
finish your studies first.

00:11:15.670 --> 00:11:17.200
Only by laying a good foundation

00:11:18.120 --> 00:11:19.630
can you get better chances later.

00:11:20.550 --> 00:11:22.000
I've already spoken to the school.

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:23.150
You can go back anytime.

00:11:23.670 --> 00:11:24.320
I don't want to.

00:11:24.790 --> 00:11:25.720
Why not?

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:27.510
Is this about dignity?

00:11:27.910 --> 00:11:29.150
The whole thing

00:11:29.150 --> 00:11:30.840
was just a dirty scheme planned by

00:11:31.030 --> 00:11:32.000
Han Bin and Han Shuang.

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:33.600
You're the victim.

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:35.390
Everything is clear now.

00:11:35.630 --> 00:11:36.910
The school gave Han Bin

00:11:37.270 --> 00:11:38.360
a serious warning.

00:11:39.670 --> 00:11:40.910
Why don't you resume your studies?

00:11:41.390 --> 00:11:42.790
I believe no one will

00:11:42.790 --> 00:11:44.840
look at you strangely again.

00:11:46.600 --> 00:11:47.550
I make over

00:11:47.550 --> 00:11:48.790
1,000 yuan a month here,

00:11:49.390 --> 00:11:50.790
and I have a bonus
at the end of the year.

00:11:51.240 --> 00:11:52.670
It's more than your pay, right?

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:54.270
Yes, way more.

00:11:54.550 --> 00:11:55.360
But honey,

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:57.440
life isn't just about

00:11:57.480 --> 00:11:58.150
making money.

00:11:59.240 --> 00:12:01.320
If I let you drift away like this,

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:04.870
how could I face your mother?

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:10.480
Mom once said

00:12:12.600 --> 00:12:13.790
the truly respectable people

00:12:14.390 --> 00:12:15.840
are those who prove their worth

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:17.440
with their real life and efforts.

00:12:18.390 --> 00:12:19.360
For over 20 years,

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:21.120
I've enjoyed

00:12:21.150 --> 00:12:22.390
a life and education that

00:12:22.390 --> 00:12:23.240
never belonged to me.

00:12:24.910 --> 00:12:25.720
I don't want to keep

00:12:25.790 --> 00:12:27.320
depending on others.

00:12:27.510 --> 00:12:28.270
Others?

00:12:29.480 --> 00:12:30.670
Who's "others"?

00:12:31.030 --> 00:12:32.200
Would "others" take a train

00:12:32.200 --> 00:12:32.750
all the way here

00:12:32.790 --> 00:12:34.030
just to come find you?

00:12:35.320 --> 00:12:36.030
Wanzhi,

00:12:36.750 --> 00:12:37.960
since you saw me,

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:42.360
you haven't even called me Dad once.

00:12:52.870 --> 00:12:53.630
Mr. Meng,

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:56.080
thank you for raising me.

00:12:56.390 --> 00:12:57.240
Please go.

00:13:00.270 --> 00:13:00.870
Fine.

00:13:01.870 --> 00:13:02.790
Since I'm here,

00:13:03.200 --> 00:13:04.840
I must take you home.

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:05.870
Let's go!

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:06.870
Don't you dare!

00:13:07.240 --> 00:13:07.630
Come on!

00:13:07.630 --> 00:13:08.390
Stop!

00:13:09.390 --> 00:13:10.120
Fang, don't be scared!

00:13:10.750 --> 00:13:11.480
No matter what

00:13:11.550 --> 00:13:12.000
he has on you,

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:12.550
don't be scared.

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:13.360
With me here,

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:14.510
no one will bully you!

00:13:14.670 --> 00:13:16.000
Who do you think you are?

00:13:16.150 --> 00:13:17.150
Why are you forcing her

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:18.000
to leave with you?

00:13:18.150 --> 00:13:18.960
Wanzhi, don't worry.

00:13:19.150 --> 00:13:20.030
I've called the police!

00:13:20.030 --> 00:13:20.480
Yeah!

00:13:20.750 --> 00:13:21.840
You misunderstood us.

00:13:22.480 --> 00:13:23.120
He's my...

00:13:25.630 --> 00:13:26.320
father.

00:13:30.200 --> 00:13:30.670
What...

00:13:32.870 --> 00:13:34.150
I really didn't expect

00:13:35.750 --> 00:13:36.870
you'd made so many friends

00:13:36.870 --> 00:13:37.960
here already.

00:13:38.320 --> 00:13:39.030
No wonder you don't

00:13:39.030 --> 00:13:39.840
want to go back.

00:13:40.270 --> 00:13:41.960
Oh, sir!

00:13:42.270 --> 00:13:44.030
I'm sorry. We got it wrong!

00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:45.000
It's okay.

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:46.270
Sorry for the scene.

00:13:47.390 --> 00:13:48.440
With friends like you

00:13:48.440 --> 00:13:49.360
around her,

00:13:50.720 --> 00:13:51.480
I can rest my mind.

00:13:52.270 --> 00:13:52.870
Sir,

00:13:53.440 --> 00:13:54.750
you two continue. We'll go.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:55.240
Sure.

00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:55.630
Zhu,

00:13:55.670 --> 00:13:56.200
come on!

00:13:56.320 --> 00:13:56.960
Hurry!

00:13:57.390 --> 00:13:58.270
Fang, call me if necessary.

00:13:58.480 --> 00:13:59.080
I'll be here!

00:13:59.480 --> 00:14:00.480
Be here for what?

00:14:00.550 --> 00:14:01.960
Read the room, alright?

00:14:02.030 --> 00:14:02.550
Just go!

00:14:13.870 --> 00:14:15.120
You're not coming back with me?

00:14:16.480 --> 00:14:17.630
I'm not a kid anymore.

00:14:18.790 --> 00:14:20.200
Coming to Shenzhen to build a life

00:14:21.630 --> 00:14:22.790
is my own choice.

00:14:24.550 --> 00:14:25.600
I want to choose

00:14:27.030 --> 00:14:28.150
my life and my fate myself.

00:14:31.150 --> 00:14:32.200
Working to

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:33.270
prove yourself...

00:14:34.910 --> 00:14:35.550
I support that.

00:14:36.510 --> 00:14:37.000
How about this?

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:39.870
Let's make a deal for one year.

00:14:41.030 --> 00:14:42.600
If you can't settle in Shenzhen

00:14:43.000 --> 00:14:44.750
and find a place suitable for you,

00:14:46.790 --> 00:14:48.240
you'll go back and finish college.

00:14:49.150 --> 00:14:49.720
What do you say?

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:52.600
Okay.

00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:09.240
Although you make more money than me,

00:15:09.840 --> 00:15:11.440
Shenzhen is different from inland.

00:15:11.840 --> 00:15:12.670
Living costs are high.

00:15:15.630 --> 00:15:16.120
Take this.

00:15:16.390 --> 00:15:17.080
I can't take it.

00:15:17.390 --> 00:15:18.360
I know you've spent

00:15:18.360 --> 00:15:19.960
all the money your mom left you.

00:15:20.600 --> 00:15:21.200
I can't.

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:22.150
Just take it.

00:15:22.390 --> 00:15:23.150
No.

00:15:24.480 --> 00:15:26.030
I really can't.

00:15:26.480 --> 00:15:27.510
I have a salary.

00:15:27.670 --> 00:15:28.910
I can support myself.

00:15:32.870 --> 00:15:33.750
Then I'm going back.

00:15:35.510 --> 00:15:36.480
If I get going now,

00:15:36.840 --> 00:15:37.750
I can catch the earliest

00:15:37.790 --> 00:15:38.750
train back to Guizhou.

00:15:39.840 --> 00:15:40.270
I'm leaving.

00:15:44.120 --> 00:15:44.550
Wait!

00:15:47.510 --> 00:15:48.670
If you don't mind

00:15:48.960 --> 00:15:49.840
the place,

00:15:50.080 --> 00:15:51.320
stay for lunch.

00:15:52.000 --> 00:15:52.840
I'll cook for you.

00:15:53.600 --> 00:15:54.440
You can cook?

00:15:55.080 --> 00:15:56.030
I'm still learning.

00:15:56.600 --> 00:15:57.600
That's progress at least.

00:15:58.360 --> 00:15:59.720
I'd love to try your cooking,

00:16:00.720 --> 00:16:02.200
but I don't have time today.

00:16:04.240 --> 00:16:04.960
Maybe next time.

00:16:17.150 --> 00:16:18.510
I'll come back to see you when I'm free.

00:16:19.840 --> 00:16:21.240
Remember to call

00:16:21.320 --> 00:16:21.960
and write to us.

00:16:24.080 --> 00:16:24.870
Grandma Yu

00:16:27.120 --> 00:16:28.120
is worried about you.

00:16:31.320 --> 00:16:32.000
You can go back now.

00:16:32.670 --> 00:16:33.270
I

00:16:35.720 --> 00:16:36.240
have to go.

00:17:09.510 --> 00:17:10.880
I'm not lying.

00:17:11.440 --> 00:17:13.160
I'm really from the mountains.

00:17:13.680 --> 00:17:14.640
He's my...

00:17:15.270 --> 00:17:15.880
Godfather?

00:17:17.510 --> 00:17:18.240
What?

00:17:18.920 --> 00:17:19.720
Foster father.

00:17:20.790 --> 00:17:22.000
That's what I meant.

00:17:22.070 --> 00:17:23.790
I just didn't say it right.

00:17:24.480 --> 00:17:26.110
Honestly, I don't get you.

00:17:26.830 --> 00:17:29.270
If I had a vice mayor for

00:17:29.680 --> 00:17:30.440
a foster father,

00:17:30.920 --> 00:17:32.550
I'd never go back to the mountains

00:17:32.550 --> 00:17:33.480
to look for my real dad.

00:17:33.590 --> 00:17:34.960
He abandoned you!

00:17:35.030 --> 00:17:35.880
I really...

00:17:36.440 --> 00:17:37.680
don't know what to say to you.

00:17:38.270 --> 00:17:39.070
Alright, alright!

00:17:39.510 --> 00:17:40.480
Pack your things

00:17:40.880 --> 00:17:42.480
and go back to be a rich young lady!

00:17:43.270 --> 00:17:43.920
Then the two of us

00:17:43.920 --> 00:17:45.480
won't have to work in Shenzhen.

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:47.480
We can go work

00:17:47.720 --> 00:17:49.070
in your dad's big project.

00:17:49.310 --> 00:17:50.720
It's okay if they pay less.

00:17:50.880 --> 00:17:52.110
What matters more is that

00:17:52.160 --> 00:17:53.240
they can give us a stable job.

00:17:54.480 --> 00:17:56.200
He's actually really good to me.

00:17:57.310 --> 00:17:58.550
But today...

00:18:00.550 --> 00:18:02.350
I couldn't bring myself to call him Dad.

00:18:03.510 --> 00:18:04.880
I... I'm afraid...

00:18:07.110 --> 00:18:09.160
I'll never be able to.

00:18:35.160 --> 00:18:35.830
Li Juan!

00:18:36.480 --> 00:18:37.000
Li Juan!

00:18:37.160 --> 00:18:38.240
What are you yelling for?

00:18:38.350 --> 00:18:39.270
Don't you see I'm busy?

00:18:40.030 --> 00:18:41.160
Captain Zhou is here!

00:18:42.240 --> 00:18:43.200
If you don't want to see him,

00:18:43.270 --> 00:18:44.720
I'll tell him you're busy.

00:18:45.960 --> 00:18:46.750
When did I say that?

00:19:00.480 --> 00:19:01.110
Fang,

00:19:03.310 --> 00:19:03.960
you okay?

00:19:05.350 --> 00:19:05.750
Yeah.

00:19:08.270 --> 00:19:09.310
Who's Captain Zhou?

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:10.680
Why do you care?

00:19:10.750 --> 00:19:12.270
Hey, what's with the attitude?

00:19:12.830 --> 00:19:14.000
You tried to hit on him and failed.

00:19:14.200 --> 00:19:14.920
Now she can't ask?

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:16.750
What do you mean "failed"?

00:19:16.960 --> 00:19:17.920
I was the one who

00:19:17.920 --> 00:19:19.070
turned him down.

00:19:20.070 --> 00:19:20.960
Stop bragging.

00:19:21.070 --> 00:19:22.200
Did he ever even like you?

00:19:22.350 --> 00:19:23.110
Say that again?

00:19:26.440 --> 00:19:27.590
She's just jealous.

00:19:28.270 --> 00:19:29.070
We used to cook

00:19:29.070 --> 00:19:30.110
for the engineering soldiers

00:19:30.440 --> 00:19:30.960
and served

00:19:31.030 --> 00:19:31.960
Captain Zhou's unit.

00:19:48.680 --> 00:19:49.750
My superior talked to me.

00:19:52.750 --> 00:19:54.680
After this support mission,

00:19:55.000 --> 00:19:56.000
I'll be decommissioned.

00:19:56.590 --> 00:19:57.400
So it's

00:19:57.830 --> 00:19:59.000
less than half a year left.

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:01.510
I hope

00:20:02.310 --> 00:20:03.240
to make

00:20:03.680 --> 00:20:05.110
our relationship official
before I leave.

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:07.680
It's so sudden.

00:20:09.550 --> 00:20:10.480
I haven't decided yet.

00:20:12.790 --> 00:20:13.310
So

00:20:15.350 --> 00:20:16.440
how much time do you need?

00:20:17.510 --> 00:20:18.480
Decide what?

00:20:18.880 --> 00:20:20.880
You think you're too
good for Zhou Shuchun?

00:20:21.750 --> 00:20:23.510
Stop aiming higher than you can reach.

00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:25.350
You're so full of yourself.

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:26.480
I think,

00:20:26.480 --> 00:20:29.160
in your Northeast dialect,

00:20:29.640 --> 00:20:30.640
you're just

00:20:31.240 --> 00:20:32.750
putting on ears.

00:20:33.110 --> 00:20:34.480
What ears?

00:20:34.550 --> 00:20:35.480
It's putting on airs.

00:20:35.640 --> 00:20:37.000
Yeah, that's you.

00:20:40.590 --> 00:20:41.270
Maybe

00:20:41.680 --> 00:20:43.160
you can tell Mr. Zhou

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:45.160
that I have nothing to decide about

00:20:45.510 --> 00:20:47.270
and that I can find him tomorrow.

00:20:47.680 --> 00:20:49.030
Stop messing around.

00:20:49.110 --> 00:20:50.240
I'm only hesitating because

00:20:50.310 --> 00:20:51.270
of my family conditions.

00:20:54.790 --> 00:20:55.350
Wanzhi,

00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:57.240
you're well-educated.

00:20:57.240 --> 00:20:58.480
Give me some advice.

00:20:58.830 --> 00:21:00.240
What's wrong with your family?

00:21:05.480 --> 00:21:06.270
I have

00:21:07.920 --> 00:21:09.000
two younger sisters

00:21:09.720 --> 00:21:10.310
and a brother.

00:21:11.270 --> 00:21:12.030
They're all kids.

00:21:12.640 --> 00:21:13.310
Back then,

00:21:14.160 --> 00:21:15.480
my parents were fined for having

00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:16.880
too many children.

00:21:17.510 --> 00:21:18.790
And now my dad is sick

00:21:19.680 --> 00:21:20.960
and can't work in the fields.

00:21:22.160 --> 00:21:23.480
My mom alone

00:21:24.960 --> 00:21:25.510
can't support

00:21:25.550 --> 00:21:26.750
the whole family.

00:21:27.720 --> 00:21:28.400
That's why

00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:29.680
she sends every penny she makes

00:21:29.790 --> 00:21:30.880
home every month.

00:21:33.440 --> 00:21:36.310
I'm worried that if I get married,

00:21:37.200 --> 00:21:38.640
I can't send money home anymore.

00:21:39.400 --> 00:21:40.920
Then what will happen to my parents,

00:21:40.920 --> 00:21:41.960
my brother and sisters?

00:21:43.640 --> 00:21:44.880
Just put that aside.

00:21:45.920 --> 00:21:47.110
What do you think of

00:21:47.110 --> 00:21:47.680
Mr. Zhou?

00:21:48.030 --> 00:21:49.240
He's a great guy.

00:21:49.750 --> 00:21:51.240
Highly respected in the army.

00:21:52.590 --> 00:21:53.350
Actually,

00:21:53.720 --> 00:21:55.160
I've dreamed about the moment

00:21:58.310 --> 00:22:00.160
of him coming to me like this.

00:22:00.750 --> 00:22:03.400
I've dreamed about it as well.

00:22:03.830 --> 00:22:04.880
If I had known this,

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:05.640
I wouldn't have come

00:22:05.680 --> 00:22:06.960
to this construction site with you.

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:07.960
If I still worked

00:22:07.960 --> 00:22:08.880
at the old site...

00:22:09.030 --> 00:22:09.960
After you left,

00:22:10.160 --> 00:22:11.200
maybe Mr. Zhou

00:22:11.240 --> 00:22:12.200
would be interested in me.

00:22:12.590 --> 00:22:13.880
Get lost!

00:22:17.590 --> 00:22:18.070
Wanzhi,

00:22:18.920 --> 00:22:20.070
help me out.

00:22:21.240 --> 00:22:22.200
I think you should

00:22:22.310 --> 00:22:23.680
tell him everything
you're worried about.

00:22:24.030 --> 00:22:24.830
Don't hide anything.

00:22:25.160 --> 00:22:25.960
Then see how he reacts.

00:22:26.550 --> 00:22:27.480
You can't do that!

00:22:27.880 --> 00:22:28.590
What if he changes

00:22:28.720 --> 00:22:29.680
his mind hearing her?

00:22:30.160 --> 00:22:31.680
Everyone has his own family.

00:22:32.030 --> 00:22:32.960
That's fate.

00:22:34.070 --> 00:22:34.960
No one can choose

00:22:35.070 --> 00:22:36.030
their parents.

00:22:37.070 --> 00:22:38.200
Being honest is not only

00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:39.790
being responsible for the relationship,

00:22:40.070 --> 00:22:41.640
but also the foundation of mutual trust.

00:22:43.240 --> 00:22:45.310
College students really are different.

00:22:46.510 --> 00:22:47.240
Thank you.

00:22:47.790 --> 00:22:48.960
You two fools.

00:22:49.350 --> 00:22:50.720
If you ask me, I'll suggest you

00:22:50.790 --> 00:22:52.350
grab a good man like him first.

00:22:52.920 --> 00:22:54.510
Don't tell him about your family yet.

00:22:54.640 --> 00:22:55.640
Just enjoy dating

00:22:55.750 --> 00:22:57.270
and take it to the next level.

00:22:57.550 --> 00:22:58.550
If he dares back out,

00:22:58.720 --> 00:22:59.960
I'll go complain to his superior!

00:23:00.000 --> 00:23:01.400
Hao Qianqian,

00:23:02.400 --> 00:23:03.640
I started to work at 13,

00:23:03.750 --> 00:23:05.200
and I've seen a lot of things.

00:23:05.310 --> 00:23:06.550
But I can never be like you.

00:23:06.680 --> 00:23:07.880
I can't do what

00:23:08.110 --> 00:23:08.880
you suggest.

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:10.000
Useless.

00:23:10.680 --> 00:23:12.110
And you, Fang Wanzhi,

00:23:12.440 --> 00:23:13.310
don't act like

00:23:13.400 --> 00:23:14.400
you've been through this.

00:23:14.750 --> 00:23:15.750
You gave her the advice.

00:23:15.790 --> 00:23:16.750
But if it doesn't work out,

00:23:17.240 --> 00:23:17.960
it'll be your fault.

00:23:18.270 --> 00:23:19.880
You have to stick to your principles.

00:23:20.440 --> 00:23:22.000
Just be honest with the man you love.

00:23:22.200 --> 00:23:23.000
No matter what,

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:24.680
I think that's the right thing to do.

00:23:25.000 --> 00:23:26.640
I don't get all that fancy stuff.

00:23:27.200 --> 00:23:28.510
Juan, I'm only looking out for you.

00:23:28.680 --> 00:23:29.440
Just listen to me.

00:23:29.790 --> 00:23:30.960
I agree with Wanzhi.

00:23:32.160 --> 00:23:32.640
You...

00:23:34.750 --> 00:23:35.550
Fine.

00:23:35.830 --> 00:23:36.640
If you and Mr. Zhou

00:23:36.640 --> 00:23:37.440
don't end up together,

00:23:37.640 --> 00:23:38.270
I'll take him.

00:23:52.720 --> 00:23:58.030
♪There's a girl in the village
named Fang♪

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:09.750
♪There's a girl in the village
named Fang♪

00:24:15.160 --> 00:24:15.830
Hello, Zhu.

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:16.880
Fang,

00:24:19.440 --> 00:24:20.310
well, I've asked around.

00:24:20.550 --> 00:24:21.550
Shenzhen is a place with

00:24:22.030 --> 00:24:22.720
various medicines.

00:24:23.590 --> 00:24:25.400
I picked the expensive ones
and bought two kinds.

00:24:26.070 --> 00:24:26.830
What medicine?

00:24:27.680 --> 00:24:28.270
Dramamine.

00:24:29.200 --> 00:24:29.920
Don't you get carsick?

00:24:33.880 --> 00:24:35.000
I'm sorry, Zhu.

00:24:36.000 --> 00:24:37.510
One really shouldn't lie.

00:24:37.750 --> 00:24:39.160
I even forgot my own excuse.

00:24:43.590 --> 00:24:44.550
You don't get carsick?

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:48.830
Then...

00:24:48.830 --> 00:24:49.830
let's go buy groceries today.

00:24:50.830 --> 00:24:53.030
Li Juan, Qian, and I planned it

00:24:53.110 --> 00:24:53.960
out yesterday.

00:24:54.070 --> 00:24:55.000
We'll take turns.

00:24:55.270 --> 00:24:56.200
Today's Li Juan's turn.

00:24:57.720 --> 00:24:58.400
Can't you

00:24:59.110 --> 00:25:00.110
go with me today instead?

00:25:01.590 --> 00:25:02.830
Li Juan has business to do.

00:25:02.830 --> 00:25:04.510
She's going to Mr. Zhou's site.

00:25:04.920 --> 00:25:06.000
You can drop her off

00:25:06.030 --> 00:25:07.640
and pick her up after buying groceries.

00:25:08.480 --> 00:25:09.350
But thanks, Zhu!

00:25:19.070 --> 00:25:19.750
So

00:25:20.550 --> 00:25:22.830
does this mean we're
officially a couple?

00:25:30.790 --> 00:25:32.240
Hey, everyone's watching.

00:25:33.350 --> 00:25:33.880
Come on.

00:25:34.270 --> 00:25:35.240
What are you afraid of?

00:25:36.110 --> 00:25:37.480
They all know I like you.

00:25:38.440 --> 00:25:39.200
I need to tell them.

00:25:40.720 --> 00:25:41.960
Comrades of the Sixth Company!

00:25:45.160 --> 00:25:46.550
I just won my

00:25:47.510 --> 00:25:48.270
personal battle!

00:25:48.480 --> 00:25:50.830
Greetings, ma'am!

00:25:52.200 --> 00:25:53.110
What are they shouting?

00:25:53.510 --> 00:25:54.720
The boys are saying hello.

00:25:56.960 --> 00:25:58.030
She didn't hear it clearly.

00:25:58.590 --> 00:25:59.350
Say it again!

00:25:59.960 --> 00:26:00.640
Louder!

00:26:00.960 --> 00:26:01.640
On my command.

00:26:02.240 --> 00:26:02.720
One...

00:26:03.310 --> 00:26:03.830
Two!

00:26:04.160 --> 00:26:07.110
Greetings, ma'am!

00:26:08.640 --> 00:26:09.510
Hug her!

00:26:09.880 --> 00:26:15.400
Hug her...

00:26:17.830 --> 00:26:21.590
Kiss...

00:26:21.590 --> 00:26:22.270
Knock it off!

00:26:22.830 --> 00:26:23.480
This is a work site,

00:26:23.960 --> 00:26:24.960
not a wedding chamber!

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:26.440
Break time's over!

00:26:26.720 --> 00:26:27.480
Back to work!

00:26:39.200 --> 00:26:39.750
Juan?

00:26:40.880 --> 00:26:41.480
Juan!

00:26:42.160 --> 00:26:42.750
Coming!

00:26:43.720 --> 00:26:44.920
Hurry!

00:26:45.750 --> 00:26:46.880
We're waiting!

00:26:47.110 --> 00:26:47.720
Come on!

00:26:47.880 --> 00:26:48.750
Tell us everything!

00:26:52.880 --> 00:26:53.510
Actually,

00:26:54.440 --> 00:26:56.000
our families are about the same.

00:26:56.510 --> 00:26:57.880
His mother has eye problems.

00:26:58.000 --> 00:26:58.720
It's really bad.

00:26:59.590 --> 00:27:00.880
She almost can't see.

00:27:01.270 --> 00:27:02.110
He was worried I'd leave

00:27:02.110 --> 00:27:02.880
him if I found out.

00:27:03.550 --> 00:27:05.400
A blind mother-in-law?

00:27:05.960 --> 00:27:07.480
You'll suffer then.

00:27:07.830 --> 00:27:09.030
But it depends

00:27:09.070 --> 00:27:09.880
on her health.

00:27:09.960 --> 00:27:10.880
It's okay if she's fragile.

00:27:11.200 --> 00:27:12.480
Hao Qianqian, have some decency,

00:27:12.480 --> 00:27:13.310
alright?

00:27:13.680 --> 00:27:14.350
You'll have to look

00:27:14.440 --> 00:27:15.110
after her for years.

00:27:15.240 --> 00:27:16.270
I hope she lives a long life.

00:27:16.400 --> 00:27:17.880
I don't mind taking care of her.

00:27:18.310 --> 00:27:20.270
I hope you won't regret it.

00:27:20.480 --> 00:27:21.750
I won't.

00:27:23.070 --> 00:27:24.000
Mr. Zhou said

00:27:26.510 --> 00:27:27.640
no matter how heavy

00:27:27.830 --> 00:27:29.270
our family burdens are,

00:27:30.510 --> 00:27:31.790
as long as we're together,

00:27:32.550 --> 00:27:34.160
we can overcome the obstacles.

00:27:35.720 --> 00:27:37.440
You're so cheesy!

00:27:37.590 --> 00:27:38.640
A few nice words,

00:27:38.640 --> 00:27:39.550
and you got carried away.

00:27:41.590 --> 00:27:42.240
Li Juan,

00:27:43.350 --> 00:27:44.680
I wish you happiness.

00:27:47.440 --> 00:27:49.350
I wish you

00:27:50.030 --> 00:27:51.160
a life without hardship.

00:27:52.510 --> 00:27:53.790
As long as I'm with him,

00:27:54.550 --> 00:27:55.510
I don't mind a life

00:27:55.960 --> 00:27:56.720
of hardship.

00:27:57.830 --> 00:27:58.270
Great.

00:28:10.640 --> 00:28:11.720
So Mr. Zhou

00:28:12.070 --> 00:28:13.510
and Li Juan are officially a couple?

00:28:14.510 --> 00:28:15.000
Yes.

00:28:18.880 --> 00:28:19.920
I'm 26 now.

00:28:20.960 --> 00:28:22.270
My big brother got married

00:28:22.590 --> 00:28:23.310
when he was 21.

00:28:27.750 --> 00:28:29.000
My dad made a smart choice.

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:31.160
He was the head cook at

00:28:31.240 --> 00:28:32.200
a state-owned factory

00:28:32.590 --> 00:28:33.790
with decent pay.

00:28:34.270 --> 00:28:36.030
But when they wouldn't
let me take over his job,

00:28:36.240 --> 00:28:37.160
he quit

00:28:37.640 --> 00:28:39.000
and brought me to Shenzhen.

00:28:39.480 --> 00:28:40.440
I didn't let him down.

00:28:41.030 --> 00:28:42.640
I became a pasta chef at 17

00:28:42.960 --> 00:28:43.830
and got my pastry chef

00:28:43.830 --> 00:28:44.960
certificate at 18.

00:28:45.440 --> 00:28:46.480
When I was 20,

00:28:46.920 --> 00:28:47.680
my father and I started

00:28:47.680 --> 00:28:48.640
running the cafeteria.

00:28:50.640 --> 00:28:51.880
I've been earning money for 10 years

00:28:52.550 --> 00:28:53.590
and saved quite a bit.

00:28:57.350 --> 00:28:57.960
Fang,

00:28:59.240 --> 00:29:00.510
your dad

00:29:01.070 --> 00:29:02.200
seems in civil service.

00:29:03.310 --> 00:29:04.830
Why didn't he pay for
you to finish college?

00:29:06.550 --> 00:29:07.680
He's my foster father.

00:29:08.750 --> 00:29:09.310
That makes sense.

00:29:09.830 --> 00:29:11.030
He only wanted to raise you.

00:29:12.110 --> 00:29:13.200
So he let you come to Shenzhen

00:29:13.920 --> 00:29:15.200
to pay him back?

00:29:16.880 --> 00:29:17.640
Sort of.

00:29:18.510 --> 00:29:19.200
Did you pay him?

00:29:19.590 --> 00:29:20.350
I can help you out.

00:29:21.350 --> 00:29:21.960
No, no.

00:29:22.400 --> 00:29:22.920
Thank you.

00:29:27.270 --> 00:29:28.480
Actually,

00:29:28.880 --> 00:29:30.350
a girl's family situation
doesn't matter.

00:29:31.480 --> 00:29:32.400
She just has to be kind.

00:29:33.200 --> 00:29:34.790
My parents only care about

00:29:35.400 --> 00:29:36.720
whether she can settle down with me.

00:29:39.000 --> 00:29:40.030
So that's what you want

00:29:40.240 --> 00:29:41.310
in your future wife.

00:29:41.640 --> 00:29:42.310
I'll remember that.

00:29:42.720 --> 00:29:43.590
If I find someone good,

00:29:43.790 --> 00:29:44.550
I'll fix you two up.

00:30:25.110 --> 00:30:27.030
Same for everyone!

00:30:27.240 --> 00:30:28.510
Soy milk for today.

00:30:28.720 --> 00:30:30.270
And with a smile.

00:30:31.680 --> 00:30:32.480
Add sugar yourself.

00:31:13.110 --> 00:31:13.480
Which one?

00:31:14.030 --> 00:31:15.720
- Tomatoes with eggs.
- Okay.

00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:24.480
Have some tea.

00:31:24.920 --> 00:31:25.550
Thanks.

00:31:26.590 --> 00:31:27.030
Juan.

00:31:30.160 --> 00:31:31.480
You're even calling her that now!

00:31:31.960 --> 00:31:33.070
But I'm telling you.

00:31:33.480 --> 00:31:34.830
Although you're older than me,

00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:36.440
I'll consider you my younger brother.

00:31:37.110 --> 00:31:37.550
Sure.

00:31:38.550 --> 00:31:39.270
I'll go with Juan.

00:31:39.590 --> 00:31:40.240
Whatever you want.

00:31:41.400 --> 00:31:42.720
Thank you for treating us!

00:31:44.110 --> 00:31:45.070
I should thank you, Fang.

00:31:45.310 --> 00:31:46.000
I heard about the advice

00:31:46.000 --> 00:31:46.680
you gave Juan.

00:31:47.440 --> 00:31:48.440
I admire how educated you are,

00:31:48.880 --> 00:31:49.790
and I agree with you.

00:31:51.680 --> 00:31:53.240
We met here in Shenzhen.

00:31:53.750 --> 00:31:54.200
So...

00:31:54.750 --> 00:31:55.350
I want to propose:

00:31:58.070 --> 00:31:58.640
the first cup

00:31:59.440 --> 00:32:01.720
to this city of innovation
and hard work.

00:32:04.480 --> 00:32:05.200
Wait, wait!

00:32:06.110 --> 00:32:07.680
You're treating us,

00:32:08.070 --> 00:32:08.830
but not with drinks?

00:32:10.510 --> 00:32:11.350
Excuse me.

00:32:11.680 --> 00:32:12.400
Rules in the army.

00:32:13.440 --> 00:32:13.960
How about this?

00:32:14.200 --> 00:32:14.830
You drink wine,

00:32:15.270 --> 00:32:16.400
and I have tea instead.

00:32:16.680 --> 00:32:17.830
No, no need!

00:32:18.030 --> 00:32:18.750
Too much trouble.

00:32:18.960 --> 00:32:19.750
It's okay.

00:32:20.240 --> 00:32:20.680
Cheers!

00:32:21.440 --> 00:32:21.920
Cheers!

00:32:29.200 --> 00:32:31.000
You're really splurging today!

00:32:31.270 --> 00:32:32.830
I love seafood!

00:32:32.960 --> 00:32:33.510
Can I go

00:32:33.590 --> 00:32:34.640
all out and eat?

00:32:35.270 --> 00:32:36.000
Of course.

00:32:36.680 --> 00:32:38.160
You're Juan's best friends.

00:32:38.310 --> 00:32:39.270
It's my treat.

00:32:40.960 --> 00:32:41.790
I think we have

00:32:41.880 --> 00:32:43.030
three days off this month.

00:32:43.160 --> 00:32:44.400
All construction sites are closed.

00:32:44.880 --> 00:32:46.480
Aren't you coming to find Juan

00:32:46.680 --> 00:32:47.750
and treat us again?

00:32:48.720 --> 00:32:49.310
What?

00:32:49.680 --> 00:32:50.270
Unfortunately,

00:32:50.920 --> 00:32:51.750
I'll go back to the army

00:32:51.880 --> 00:32:52.350
for a report.

00:32:52.510 --> 00:32:53.510
I won't be in town these days.

00:32:55.440 --> 00:32:56.590
So you two just got together

00:32:56.590 --> 00:32:58.030
and already have to separate?

00:32:58.270 --> 00:32:58.640
Parting is

00:32:58.640 --> 00:33:00.350
only for a better reunion.

00:33:01.350 --> 00:33:01.960
Mr. Zhou,

00:33:02.310 --> 00:33:03.550
have a safe trip.

00:33:04.240 --> 00:33:05.350
It's rare to have time off.

00:33:05.750 --> 00:33:06.830
Hope you all

00:33:06.830 --> 00:33:07.790
have a meaningful holiday.

00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:09.070
Thanks.

00:33:17.960 --> 00:33:19.880
Look at them.

00:33:20.790 --> 00:33:22.550
It makes me want to find someone too.

00:33:22.880 --> 00:33:24.310
I'm so tired all day.

00:33:24.590 --> 00:33:25.510
If I have a man

00:33:25.640 --> 00:33:27.110
to hold me when I get back,

00:33:27.160 --> 00:33:28.550
I'll sleep so well.

00:33:28.720 --> 00:33:30.480
Stop talking dirty.

00:33:30.550 --> 00:33:31.590
Why?

00:33:31.750 --> 00:33:32.880
It's just talk.

00:33:32.880 --> 00:33:34.350
We're all adults.

00:33:35.350 --> 00:33:36.960
Tell you the truth.

00:33:37.590 --> 00:33:38.720
The age on my ID

00:33:38.750 --> 00:33:39.720
is fake.

00:33:40.480 --> 00:33:41.640
I'm 26 actually.

00:33:41.830 --> 00:33:43.110
Why can't I think about men?

00:33:43.680 --> 00:33:44.480
Just think secretly.

00:33:44.720 --> 00:33:45.960
Keep it to yourself.

00:33:46.200 --> 00:33:47.720
I must say it out loud!

00:33:47.960 --> 00:33:49.070
Li Juan's off having fun

00:33:49.200 --> 00:33:50.270
with Mr. Zhou now.

00:33:50.400 --> 00:33:51.350
If I don't say it,

00:33:51.750 --> 00:33:52.880
I'll feel uncomfortable.

00:33:59.510 --> 00:34:00.550
We're having time off,

00:34:00.550 --> 00:34:01.790
but I'm not used to it.

00:34:02.960 --> 00:34:04.110
What took you two so long?

00:34:04.510 --> 00:34:06.110
You... you...

00:34:07.000 --> 00:34:07.750
What?

00:34:09.510 --> 00:34:10.880
Aren't you supposed to be with Zhou?

00:34:10.960 --> 00:34:11.760
Why are you back?

00:34:12.280 --> 00:34:13.800
I thought you'd stay overnight.

00:34:15.230 --> 00:34:15.840
Wanzhi,

00:34:16.550 --> 00:34:17.800
how come you're as bad as her?

00:34:18.920 --> 00:34:19.670
Come on.

00:34:19.760 --> 00:34:21.360
You two are officially a couple.

00:34:21.590 --> 00:34:22.230
Isn't that...

00:34:22.880 --> 00:34:25.000
normal to do it?

00:34:26.920 --> 00:34:27.880
But Zhou said

00:34:29.030 --> 00:34:30.320
we must get married first.

00:34:32.440 --> 00:34:33.000
Is there really

00:34:33.030 --> 00:34:34.280
such a pure man in this world?

00:34:34.320 --> 00:34:35.630
I can't believe it.

00:34:36.110 --> 00:34:37.320
So I took his sheets

00:34:37.320 --> 00:34:38.440
and covers

00:34:38.670 --> 00:34:39.360
and washed them

00:34:39.510 --> 00:34:40.150
while he's away.

00:34:42.400 --> 00:34:43.550
Then I have to

00:34:43.550 --> 00:34:45.230
interrogate you.

00:34:46.440 --> 00:34:48.360
How far

00:34:48.880 --> 00:34:51.030
did you two go?

00:34:51.150 --> 00:34:52.280
Did you...

00:34:55.110 --> 00:34:56.230
Why are you curious about details?

00:34:56.400 --> 00:34:56.960
I have to

00:34:56.960 --> 00:34:58.030
know details about you two.

00:34:58.150 --> 00:34:59.230
He is a man, after all.

00:34:59.280 --> 00:35:00.360
How could he be like that?

00:35:02.920 --> 00:35:03.880
Is something wrong with him?

00:35:05.510 --> 00:35:06.630
Shut up!

00:35:06.840 --> 00:35:07.840
He's perfectly normal.

00:35:08.800 --> 00:35:09.800
Did you check him?

00:35:10.710 --> 00:35:11.550
Hao Qianqian!

00:35:11.550 --> 00:35:12.360
She checked it!

00:35:12.630 --> 00:35:14.320
You... Qian, what do you...

00:35:14.400 --> 00:35:14.840
Hey!

00:35:15.030 --> 00:35:16.360
- You...
- Why are you panicking?

00:35:16.480 --> 00:35:18.110
Hey, what does it concern you?

00:35:18.590 --> 00:35:19.710
She's not concerned.

00:35:19.800 --> 00:35:20.670
She's jealous.

00:35:20.670 --> 00:35:21.190
Who said that?

00:35:21.190 --> 00:35:21.760
Hey!

00:35:22.150 --> 00:35:22.880
Hao Qianqian!

00:35:23.000 --> 00:35:24.960
How can you say that?

00:35:25.710 --> 00:35:26.880
Come catch me! Come on!

00:35:27.070 --> 00:35:28.400
That's too much!

00:35:32.230 --> 00:35:34.150
The cafeteria is closed
for the three-day holiday.

00:35:34.710 --> 00:35:35.440
The higher-ups

00:35:35.480 --> 00:35:36.840
are pretty nice to us.

00:35:37.710 --> 00:35:39.000
What do you guys want to do these days?

00:35:39.030 --> 00:35:40.070
Any plans?

00:35:40.670 --> 00:35:42.480
I actually want to go to the library.

00:35:43.070 --> 00:35:43.510
What?

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:45.000
But I know you won't like it.

00:35:45.550 --> 00:35:46.550
So I'll go with your plans.

00:35:46.880 --> 00:35:47.960
I've been here for two years

00:35:48.070 --> 00:35:49.510
and haven't visited anywhere.

00:35:49.920 --> 00:35:51.190
I heard Window of the World

00:35:51.230 --> 00:35:52.280
is really famous.

00:35:52.480 --> 00:35:53.480
I wonder what it's like.

00:35:53.710 --> 00:35:55.670
It's a park with all
the global landmarks.

00:35:55.840 --> 00:35:56.590
It's worth visiting.

00:35:57.150 --> 00:35:58.190
Is the ticket expensive?

00:35:58.440 --> 00:35:59.710
Even if it is, it's worth it.

00:36:00.760 --> 00:36:01.360
Yeah,

00:36:01.760 --> 00:36:02.800
it's cheaper than going abroad.

00:36:03.960 --> 00:36:04.880
I

00:36:05.030 --> 00:36:06.920
want to go to the East
Lake Amusement Park.

00:36:07.320 --> 00:36:08.550
I heard they have a roller coaster.

00:36:08.590 --> 00:36:09.630
It's thrilling.

00:36:10.150 --> 00:36:11.480
Or we can go swimming

00:36:11.510 --> 00:36:12.400
at the beach.

00:36:12.550 --> 00:36:13.480
There are many foreigners

00:36:13.510 --> 00:36:14.840
in Guangdong.

00:36:15.280 --> 00:36:16.030
Maybe

00:36:16.440 --> 00:36:17.320
I can find

00:36:17.360 --> 00:36:18.550
a foreign boyfriend.

00:36:18.710 --> 00:36:19.840
Oh, come on,

00:36:20.000 --> 00:36:21.840
there you go again.

00:36:22.510 --> 00:36:23.440
Wherever we go,

00:36:23.920 --> 00:36:25.230
on the first night of the holiday,

00:36:25.360 --> 00:36:26.190
the three of us

00:36:26.190 --> 00:36:26.960
must go out

00:36:26.960 --> 00:36:27.800
and have a good drink.

00:36:28.000 --> 00:36:28.710
Get totally drunk!

00:36:28.760 --> 00:36:29.480
Agreed!

00:36:29.630 --> 00:36:30.440
Agreed!

00:36:32.510 --> 00:36:33.150
Over here! Come on!

00:36:33.630 --> 00:36:34.070
Here!

00:36:35.710 --> 00:36:36.590
The lamb skewers are ready!

00:36:38.630 --> 00:36:39.880
That's a lot of food!

00:36:40.030 --> 00:36:41.110
Not really. It's all here!

00:36:43.030 --> 00:36:44.550
FYI, I'm paying today, okay?

00:36:44.760 --> 00:36:45.840
No way, I'm paying.

00:36:46.440 --> 00:36:47.440
Mr. Zhou treated us

00:36:47.510 --> 00:36:48.710
to a fancy meal the other day.

00:36:48.920 --> 00:36:49.710
This one's cheap.

00:36:50.030 --> 00:36:50.590
When he

00:36:50.630 --> 00:36:51.920
treated you two,

00:36:52.110 --> 00:36:53.000
he didn't order drinks.

00:36:53.150 --> 00:36:54.030
I'll make up for it today.

00:36:54.360 --> 00:36:55.550
That's okay.

00:36:55.550 --> 00:36:56.960
Save your money.

00:36:58.590 --> 00:37:00.110
What's with you today, Qian?

00:37:00.280 --> 00:37:01.000
You want to pay?

00:37:01.110 --> 00:37:02.440
If you do, I won't fight you.

00:37:02.630 --> 00:37:04.440
Pay what?

00:37:04.630 --> 00:37:05.710
There are so many men here.

00:37:05.920 --> 00:37:07.320
Why should three pretty girls

00:37:07.320 --> 00:37:08.230
like us pay?

00:37:08.550 --> 00:37:10.190
We can just eat and enjoy ourselves.

00:37:10.400 --> 00:37:11.550
I'll take care of this.

00:37:12.000 --> 00:37:12.400
Cheers!

00:37:14.400 --> 00:37:15.440
Cheers!

00:37:20.510 --> 00:37:23.230
♪Sorrow deep, hearts entwined♪

00:37:23.440 --> 00:37:25.630
♪Only love fills our hearts♪

00:37:26.320 --> 00:37:29.000
♪The sea of love turns wild♪

00:37:29.150 --> 00:37:31.440
♪My true heart meets cold wind♪

00:37:32.230 --> 00:37:34.960
♪Parting ways, sky apart♪

00:37:35.150 --> 00:37:37.760
♪Will fate ever let us meet?♪

00:37:38.030 --> 00:37:42.880
♪The wind howls, crying in the storm♪

00:37:43.030 --> 00:37:48.000
♪Drifting through the crowd,
life is but a dream♪

00:37:48.590 --> 00:37:51.070
♪Deep love lives on♪

00:37:51.320 --> 00:37:53.480
♪Though eternity♪

00:37:53.920 --> 00:37:56.590
♪When snow falls and storms near♪

00:37:56.800 --> 00:37:59.440
♪May the flowers bloom in grace♪

00:37:59.630 --> 00:38:05.150
♪Not afraid of the mist
and rain along the way♪

00:38:05.440 --> 00:38:07.000
Bravo!

00:38:07.000 --> 00:38:09.230
Cheers! Cheers!

00:38:12.510 --> 00:38:13.400
Alright, boss!

00:38:14.320 --> 00:38:15.030
Come on!

00:38:15.440 --> 00:38:15.880
Coming!

00:38:16.360 --> 00:38:17.190
Their bill

00:38:17.400 --> 00:38:18.070
is on me!

00:38:18.480 --> 00:38:20.030
Bring six more beers

00:38:20.280 --> 00:38:21.150
and two dishes!

00:38:21.440 --> 00:38:21.800
Alright!

00:38:21.840 --> 00:38:22.920
Thank you, sir!

00:38:23.920 --> 00:38:25.840
- Have a good night, guys!
- Cheers, beauty!

00:38:29.480 --> 00:38:31.150
You're so crazy.

00:38:31.710 --> 00:38:32.920
Let's go somewhere else.

00:38:32.960 --> 00:38:33.880
Why?

00:38:33.880 --> 00:38:34.880
The guy already paid.

00:38:35.000 --> 00:38:35.960
Just enjoy it.

00:38:37.710 --> 00:38:38.320
Here you go!

00:38:38.590 --> 00:38:39.710
Beers from the man over there.

00:38:40.360 --> 00:38:41.440
Thank you, sir!

00:38:41.840 --> 00:38:42.480
Ladies,

00:38:42.760 --> 00:38:43.400
want anything else?

00:38:43.710 --> 00:38:45.110
Get us your

00:38:45.110 --> 00:38:46.510
best seafood!

00:38:46.920 --> 00:38:47.800
Alright, coming right up!

00:38:49.070 --> 00:38:50.400
You're really something.

00:38:50.670 --> 00:38:51.190
So what?

00:38:51.280 --> 00:38:53.150
I earn my own money.

00:38:53.670 --> 00:38:54.320
Let's drink!

00:38:54.710 --> 00:38:55.360
Hey, beautiful!

00:38:55.880 --> 00:38:56.960
Can you come

00:38:57.030 --> 00:38:57.880
and sing for us?

00:38:58.070 --> 00:38:58.760
Yeah!

00:38:59.440 --> 00:39:01.000
Sorry, she's not a singer.

00:39:01.710 --> 00:39:02.920
Ten yuan

00:39:03.590 --> 00:39:04.480
for a song, okay?

00:39:04.630 --> 00:39:06.280
Sir, we told you, she's not a singer.

00:39:07.550 --> 00:39:09.230
We don't even have a stereo.

00:39:09.280 --> 00:39:10.070
I have to sing alone.

00:39:10.110 --> 00:39:11.630
It hurts my throat.

00:39:11.840 --> 00:39:12.510
Twenty yuan!

00:39:12.800 --> 00:39:13.880
Alright.

00:39:14.150 --> 00:39:14.840
Hao Qianqian!

00:39:15.070 --> 00:39:15.480
Coming!

00:39:15.480 --> 00:39:16.710
What are you doing?

00:39:18.840 --> 00:39:20.840
What song do you want to hear, sir?

00:39:21.150 --> 00:39:22.320
What about Gathering?

00:39:22.760 --> 00:39:23.230
Okay! Great!

00:39:23.230 --> 00:39:23.960
Alright, ignore her.

00:39:24.280 --> 00:39:24.800
Let's eat.

00:39:25.440 --> 00:39:30.150
♪No matter how it ends♪

00:39:30.150 --> 00:39:34.960
♪At least we were together once♪

00:39:36.550 --> 00:39:37.880
Let's sing together.

00:39:39.800 --> 00:39:40.800
I can't sing.

00:39:41.840 --> 00:39:43.150
How can she sing?

00:39:43.920 --> 00:39:45.150
I'm not her.

00:39:45.360 --> 00:39:46.760
She's not here to sing either.

00:39:47.110 --> 00:39:48.670
She's just having fun.

00:39:50.030 --> 00:39:52.000
She charged for it!

00:39:53.030 --> 00:39:54.960
You're picking who to sing for!

00:39:55.320 --> 00:39:57.760
You respect him but not me?

00:39:58.400 --> 00:40:00.030
Hey, you're drunk.

00:40:01.070 --> 00:40:02.880
You're the one who's drunk!

00:40:03.960 --> 00:40:05.280
You're singing today!

00:40:06.070 --> 00:40:07.320
Or I'll beat you!

00:40:07.800 --> 00:40:08.550
Don't come over!

00:40:11.960 --> 00:40:12.670
Hey, man,

00:40:12.960 --> 00:40:14.150
leave the girls alone!

00:40:15.440 --> 00:40:17.190
Who the hell are you?

00:40:17.710 --> 00:40:18.760
How could you do that?

00:40:19.030 --> 00:40:20.400
He hit Mr. Gao! Let's beat him!

00:40:21.190 --> 00:40:22.280
Guys...

00:40:22.760 --> 00:40:24.190
It's a misunderstanding...

00:40:24.480 --> 00:40:25.630
He didn't mean it!

00:40:26.360 --> 00:40:27.070
He's just drunk

00:40:27.230 --> 00:40:28.030
and he lost his balance.

00:40:29.590 --> 00:40:30.440
You're drunk, right?

00:40:31.110 --> 00:40:31.480
Excuse us!

00:40:31.550 --> 00:40:32.800
Stop talking! Just come.

00:40:32.960 --> 00:40:33.630
Please excuse me!

00:40:33.920 --> 00:40:34.510
My pal is drunk.

00:40:34.670 --> 00:40:35.590
Sorry about that!

00:40:35.800 --> 00:40:37.030
Alright, alright.

00:40:37.150 --> 00:40:37.800
Come on, let's go.

00:40:38.030 --> 00:40:39.150
Alright, that's enough.

00:40:39.880 --> 00:40:40.190
You...

00:40:40.320 --> 00:40:40.710
It's okay.

00:40:40.710 --> 00:40:41.400
Everything's fine.

00:40:41.480 --> 00:40:42.800
You can sit down now. Go on.

00:40:50.480 --> 00:40:51.190
Fang Wanzhi,

00:40:51.590 --> 00:40:52.480
you're really something.

00:40:55.110 --> 00:40:56.150
He was drunk,

00:40:56.150 --> 00:40:57.630
and you were actually
going to fight him.

00:41:00.000 --> 00:41:00.710
Now I see

00:41:00.710 --> 00:41:02.070
why you didn't finish college.

00:41:02.190 --> 00:41:03.000
Did you get expelled

00:41:03.030 --> 00:41:03.880
for fighting?

00:41:08.360 --> 00:41:09.550
Wanzhi,

00:41:10.150 --> 00:41:11.360
you know him?

00:41:11.920 --> 00:41:13.280
No wonder he came to help you out.

00:41:13.480 --> 00:41:14.590
Come have a drink with us.

00:41:14.710 --> 00:41:15.550
I don't know him.

00:41:17.400 --> 00:41:18.320
Thank you.

00:41:18.960 --> 00:41:19.360
No problem.

00:41:19.440 --> 00:41:20.920
You have to thank him anyway.

00:41:21.800 --> 00:41:23.400
She wasn't like this before.

00:41:24.110 --> 00:41:25.070
She's just drunk and upset.

00:41:25.280 --> 00:41:26.280
I apologize for her.

00:41:26.440 --> 00:41:27.360
Don't worry about it.

00:41:27.670 --> 00:41:28.360
You guys continue.

00:41:29.070 --> 00:41:29.710
Thanks again!

00:41:37.190 --> 00:41:38.510
He knew your name.

00:41:38.550 --> 00:41:39.840
Why did you say you don't know him?

00:41:41.030 --> 00:41:42.400
He's just an annoying man.

00:41:43.590 --> 00:41:44.800
I can't believe we ran into him.

00:41:45.230 --> 00:41:46.590
Shenzhen isn't that big.

00:41:49.670 --> 00:41:50.960
Are you okay, Mr. Gao?

00:41:51.000 --> 00:41:52.480
Yeah, let's continue.

00:42:01.000 --> 00:42:02.400
So much money!

00:42:02.670 --> 00:42:03.920
If they hadn't messed around,

00:42:03.920 --> 00:42:05.280
I could have made even more.

00:42:06.710 --> 00:42:08.230
You actually want to sing for money?

00:42:08.280 --> 00:42:09.360
Sing by yourself if you want.

00:42:10.030 --> 00:42:11.070
I didn't do anything else.

00:42:11.070 --> 00:42:12.590
Why can't I sing for money?

00:42:13.000 --> 00:42:13.760
Men...

00:42:13.960 --> 00:42:15.440
When they get drunk, they cause trouble.

00:42:15.710 --> 00:42:16.510
When they're sober,

00:42:16.510 --> 00:42:17.150
they won't spend

00:42:17.150 --> 00:42:18.590
as freely.

00:42:19.510 --> 00:42:20.510
I didn't expect so many

00:42:20.550 --> 00:42:21.630
people at the night eateries.

00:42:21.960 --> 00:42:22.840
I don't think we should

00:42:23.000 --> 00:42:24.030
waste these three days.

00:42:24.280 --> 00:42:25.190
Let's just sing there.

00:42:25.400 --> 00:42:26.320
See how much we can earn.

00:42:26.590 --> 00:42:28.000
Don't be so annoying.

00:42:28.550 --> 00:42:29.400
Don't you see Wanzhi

00:42:29.440 --> 00:42:30.480
was terrified just now?

00:42:31.070 --> 00:42:31.880
Actually, I think

00:42:31.880 --> 00:42:32.960
she's got a point.

00:42:33.760 --> 00:42:35.280
If I had handled it gracefully,

00:42:35.590 --> 00:42:36.760
it might not have ended like that.

00:42:37.440 --> 00:42:39.760
Fang Wanzhi, what are you saying?

00:42:41.670 --> 00:42:42.480
I came to Shenzhen

00:42:42.670 --> 00:42:43.400
to work and earn

00:42:43.480 --> 00:42:44.670
money with my own hands

00:42:45.110 --> 00:42:46.760
and prove I can live well

00:42:46.960 --> 00:42:47.800
by myself.

00:42:48.670 --> 00:42:50.360
Qian taught me a lesson today.

00:42:51.280 --> 00:42:52.590
I really want to try it.